WEBVTT


00:00:17.239 --> 00:00:20.500
I promised Guangcai
I'd take good care of you all for him.

00:00:21.339 --> 00:00:22.420
Now that he's gone,

00:00:24.000 --> 00:00:27.100
I want to take Chuchu abroad.
And you, of course.

00:00:27.660 --> 00:00:29.699
You don't need to worry
about life abroad.

00:00:30.440 --> 00:00:31.600
I'll take care of everything.

00:00:33.960 --> 00:00:35.560
I really appreciate your thoughtfulness.

00:00:36.060 --> 00:00:37.159
But it's not necessary.

00:00:38.000 --> 00:00:39.840
We won't be going with you.

00:00:42.039 --> 00:00:45.640
Is there anything left here
worth holding onto for you?

00:00:50.380 --> 00:00:52.960
I just don't want to get tangled up
in your affairs anymore.

00:00:54.500 --> 00:00:58.420
The most important thing right now
is to watch over Chuchu

00:00:58.840 --> 00:00:59.740
as she grows up.

00:01:02.380 --> 00:01:05.640
If you don't agree,
Guangcai won't rest easy.

00:01:08.500 --> 00:01:10.560
- Chuchu.
- Mom.

00:01:13.019 --> 00:01:16.340
Please think it over.
After all, it's Guangcai's wish.

00:01:18.760 --> 00:01:19.840
Thanks for the kindness.

00:01:20.680 --> 00:01:22.000
But it's not what I want.

00:01:23.040 --> 00:01:25.060
- Say goodbye to her.
- Goodbye.

00:02:41.148 --> 00:02:44.551
=The Silent Rift=

00:02:44.551 --> 00:02:46.892
=Episode 16=
(The Silent Rift)

00:03:01.740 --> 00:03:02.960
So diligent.

00:03:03.400 --> 00:03:04.020
Laoer.

00:03:07.800 --> 00:03:09.800
Just you? Where's Qianqian?

00:03:10.460 --> 00:03:12.180
Qianqian is about to take Gaokao.

00:03:12.460 --> 00:03:13.680
Her mom took her home first.

00:03:20.300 --> 00:03:21.080
Officer Zhu,

00:03:24.300 --> 00:03:25.180
let's talk.

00:03:26.840 --> 00:03:29.960
Yes, he has a lot
he wants to say to you.

00:03:29.960 --> 00:03:31.620
It's mealtime now. Go on.

00:03:31.740 --> 00:03:32.400
Okay.

00:03:32.900 --> 00:03:33.680
Leave it to me.

00:03:34.060 --> 00:03:35.580
Alright. The leg massage is done.

00:03:36.280 --> 00:03:37.460
Laosan's arm is a bit stiff.

00:03:37.460 --> 00:03:38.340
Got it.

00:03:39.900 --> 00:03:40.460
Okay.

00:03:46.740 --> 00:03:47.639
Laosan,

00:03:49.400 --> 00:03:50.400
listen to me.

00:03:53.960 --> 00:03:56.580
The case is solved.
It even made the papers.

00:03:58.680 --> 00:03:59.860
Let me read it to you.

00:04:00.460 --> 00:04:02.300
"Eighteen-Year-Old Cold Case Cracked."

00:04:02.460 --> 00:04:04.460
"All Suspects Captured."

00:04:07.580 --> 00:04:08.240
Happy?

00:04:19.560 --> 00:04:22.579
Captain Li,
you picked such a fancy place.

00:04:22.959 --> 00:04:23.899
What's this about?

00:04:26.019 --> 00:04:26.800
Zhu,

00:04:31.439 --> 00:04:32.680
I owe you an apology.

00:04:38.112 --> 00:04:41.360
You know I've got a hot temper.

00:04:43.180 --> 00:04:45.500
I know I shouldn't have
treated you that way.

00:04:46.100 --> 00:04:50.120
But as you know, on this matter,
I just couldn't contain my anger.

00:04:51.379 --> 00:04:53.319
And my usual attitude
towards you was really...

00:04:56.680 --> 00:05:00.040
Actually, I know that with my master
lying there for so many years,

00:05:03.180 --> 00:05:04.180
you took it harder.

00:05:06.860 --> 00:05:08.680
But I never considered how you felt.

00:05:11.360 --> 00:05:12.160
I'm sorry.

00:05:16.600 --> 00:05:17.240
I'm sorry.

00:05:21.280 --> 00:05:22.620
Anyway,

00:05:25.680 --> 00:05:27.180
whether you forgive me or not,

00:05:28.160 --> 00:05:29.000
I'll drink.

00:05:35.220 --> 00:05:36.100
That's all?

00:05:36.540 --> 00:05:37.240
Not yet.

00:05:39.060 --> 00:05:42.040
There's one thing
I still can't figure out.

00:05:43.160 --> 00:05:45.040
Meng Guangcai

00:05:47.300 --> 00:05:48.352
suddenly confessed.

00:05:48.352 --> 00:05:50.480
What's the real reason behind this?

00:05:51.600 --> 00:05:53.420
Was it really for the kids,
as he claimed?

00:05:55.240 --> 00:05:56.100
Anyway,

00:05:57.980 --> 00:05:58.870
I feel

00:05:59.808 --> 00:06:02.420
there must be some other reason
we haven't thought of.

00:06:19.740 --> 00:06:21.860
Mr. Chen, I'm sorry.

00:06:21.860 --> 00:06:22.420
(Rongfa Noodle Shop)

00:06:22.420 --> 00:06:26.100
Guangcai and the others are tied up
with the IPO. They couldn't come.

00:06:33.100 --> 00:06:36.720
You and Xiaoliang
are heading abroad soon.

00:06:37.060 --> 00:06:39.000
It's time for me
to go back to Shaguai Village.

00:06:41.740 --> 00:06:43.600
I'll join Xiaoliang
to visit his new school.

00:06:43.920 --> 00:06:46.620
Once he's settled in,
I'll come back to see you.

00:06:46.620 --> 00:06:48.480
Don't worry about me.

00:06:49.100 --> 00:06:52.920
I've lived a long life.
I've seen it all.

00:06:55.620 --> 00:07:01.800
Qin, you are the smartest
among those kids

00:07:02.040 --> 00:07:04.240
who came from Shaguai Village.

00:07:06.300 --> 00:07:10.240
Raise Xiaoliang well.
Make sure he walks the right path.

00:07:34.800 --> 00:07:36.160
I'll take Grandpa home first.

00:07:36.812 --> 00:07:42.060
(Rongfa Noodle Shop)

00:08:42.059 --> 00:08:44.700
Principal Chen. Principal Chen, hello.

00:08:46.360 --> 00:08:48.320
- Haven't seen you in years.
- Hello.

00:08:48.320 --> 00:08:49.360
Are you doing alright?

00:08:49.360 --> 00:08:51.200
- Not bad.
- Still so spirited.

00:08:51.480 --> 00:08:52.740
I need to tell you something.

00:08:53.019 --> 00:08:56.759
The high-speed rail is coming
through our Magou Town.

00:08:57.740 --> 00:08:59.740
All these houses here
will be demolished.

00:09:00.139 --> 00:09:02.240
Actually, let me
tell you something else.

00:09:02.399 --> 00:09:06.080
Truth is, this house
hasn't been lived in since it was built.

00:09:06.740 --> 00:09:09.184
Since the house is registered

00:09:09.590 --> 00:09:11.019
under your name,

00:09:11.500 --> 00:09:14.080
how about you sign here?

00:09:15.139 --> 00:09:16.740
I support the village's plan.

00:09:16.740 --> 00:09:17.759
Thank you so much.

00:09:17.759 --> 00:09:21.940
The village just needs
to arrange a place for me to live.

00:09:21.940 --> 00:09:23.240
No problem, Principal Chen.

00:09:23.240 --> 00:09:24.620
Come on. Take it easy.

00:09:24.860 --> 00:09:25.460
Okay.

00:09:25.460 --> 00:09:30.604
(Chen Rongfa)

00:09:45.379 --> 00:09:46.600
I heard Principal Chen

00:09:50.000 --> 00:09:51.220
went back to Shaguai Village.

00:09:52.259 --> 00:09:53.820
Principal Chen is getting old.

00:09:54.500 --> 00:09:56.840
He wanted to go back,
so we had to respect his wishes.

00:10:01.460 --> 00:10:02.379
How is Xiaoliang?

00:10:03.879 --> 00:10:05.240
He drove Principal Chen home.

00:10:07.960 --> 00:10:09.019
When are you leaving?

00:10:10.639 --> 00:10:12.740
The day after tomorrow. All's set.

00:10:14.620 --> 00:10:17.500
So fast? That's good.

00:10:21.460 --> 00:10:22.820
He's doing quite well in there.

00:10:23.879 --> 00:10:24.860
He asked me

00:10:27.580 --> 00:10:28.600
to give this to you.

00:10:38.460 --> 00:10:40.220
I've never given him anything.

00:10:42.080 --> 00:10:45.639
That year, I just wanted
to get him a nice watch.

00:10:47.019 --> 00:10:48.820
I didn't expect he'd wear it till today.

00:10:50.240 --> 00:10:54.259
It's clear you're important to him.

00:11:02.460 --> 00:11:06.000
Zhu, did you call me here today
just for this?

00:11:07.340 --> 00:11:11.460
Actually, old things
can bring back many memories.

00:11:13.720 --> 00:11:15.080
But things have changed.

00:11:16.379 --> 00:11:18.220
People just can't go back.

00:11:23.100 --> 00:11:25.240
Zhu, is there anything else today?

00:11:26.120 --> 00:11:29.580
Nothing. I'm just curious.

00:11:30.820 --> 00:11:32.460
When Meng Guangcai was taken in,

00:11:33.820 --> 00:11:36.240
rushed over anxiously to find me,

00:11:37.000 --> 00:11:38.340
inquiring about the situation

00:11:38.840 --> 00:11:40.139
and defending him.

00:11:41.320 --> 00:11:43.840
Now that he's completely confessed
and volunteered the truth,

00:11:45.019 --> 00:11:48.240
you seem less concerned about him now.

00:11:54.460 --> 00:11:57.620
I never expected them
to commit that crime.

00:11:59.019 --> 00:12:00.379
Now things have come to this.

00:12:02.000 --> 00:12:03.759
I've done all I can.

00:12:08.220 --> 00:12:09.259
You should know.

00:12:10.720 --> 00:12:12.659
You're important to him, after all.

00:12:14.600 --> 00:12:15.879
Meng Guangcai has confessed

00:12:17.379 --> 00:12:20.960
that they were actually engaged
in a planned crime.

00:12:22.480 --> 00:12:25.000
It was an organized conspiracy.

00:12:25.460 --> 00:12:27.616
All the suspects' stories

00:12:28.576 --> 00:12:30.259
were prearranged.

00:12:30.960 --> 00:12:32.340
One person taught them.

00:12:33.360 --> 00:12:34.460
That's Meng Guangcai.

00:12:35.720 --> 00:12:37.860
They're a tight-knit alliance
who move together,

00:12:38.720 --> 00:12:40.759
cover for each other,

00:12:41.019 --> 00:12:42.580
and coordinate as one.

00:12:43.860 --> 00:12:45.240
This alliance is a script.

00:12:46.720 --> 00:12:48.240
It's a perfect story.

00:12:48.960 --> 00:12:51.460
Because this seemingly flawless script

00:12:54.460 --> 00:12:56.720
had me wandering aimlessly inside
for many years.

00:12:57.500 --> 00:12:59.759
Do you know the purpose of their script?

00:13:02.259 --> 00:13:03.879
I don't know what you're talking about.

00:13:04.840 --> 00:13:06.220
Their goal is very clear

00:13:07.019 --> 00:13:08.000
and it's sole.

00:13:08.960 --> 00:13:10.500
To get as many out as they can.

00:13:12.320 --> 00:13:13.820
If someone can't escape,

00:13:14.600 --> 00:13:17.960
the ones inside
will cover for the ones outside.

00:13:19.460 --> 00:13:21.220
If none can escape,

00:13:22.580 --> 00:13:25.740
then everyone will cover for one person,

00:13:27.600 --> 00:13:28.820
which is Meng Guangcai.

00:13:29.960 --> 00:13:31.139
Isn't it very logical?

00:13:33.139 --> 00:13:34.340
I'm not sure.

00:13:37.220 --> 00:13:38.080
Of course.

00:13:39.139 --> 00:13:40.220
It's logical.

00:13:41.220 --> 00:13:42.340
Because they know,

00:13:43.759 --> 00:13:45.320
as long as Meng Guangcai is there,

00:13:46.100 --> 00:13:47.552
everyone's later years

00:13:49.024 --> 00:13:51.019
might be prosperous.

00:13:52.580 --> 00:13:54.460
But everywhere there seems to be logic,

00:13:55.240 --> 00:13:57.639
something illogical always surfaces.

00:13:58.519 --> 00:13:59.879
For example, Jiao Lijun.

00:14:01.000 --> 00:14:02.740
He voluntarily put himself in here.

00:14:04.519 --> 00:14:05.740
That's very odd.

00:14:06.580 --> 00:14:07.759
For example, Xue Yonghui.

00:14:09.100 --> 00:14:10.912
He'd rather reveal his left hand

00:14:11.712 --> 00:14:13.519
and all his secrets

00:14:13.759 --> 00:14:15.960
in front of the police

00:14:18.000 --> 00:14:19.500
and still wanted Huang Mantang dead.

00:14:21.220 --> 00:14:22.500
That's very odd.

00:14:24.960 --> 00:14:26.120
So I always feel

00:14:27.500 --> 00:14:29.019
among all the truths,

00:14:30.519 --> 00:14:31.720
there is always a part

00:14:33.980 --> 00:14:35.580
that remains unclear.

00:14:36.740 --> 00:14:39.220
As if something is being hidden.

00:14:41.000 --> 00:14:43.240
Until Meng Guangcai
finally said one thing to me.

00:14:44.860 --> 00:14:48.879
He said he's never really changed.

00:14:50.460 --> 00:14:52.519
He's still the Meng Guangcai
I've always known,

00:14:53.000 --> 00:14:56.340
who is young and loyal,

00:14:56.340 --> 00:14:57.879
works with vigor,

00:14:59.340 --> 00:15:01.080
lacks scheming,

00:15:02.240 --> 00:15:03.700
doesn't play mind games,

00:15:04.460 --> 00:15:06.519
and doesn't like planning.

00:15:08.519 --> 00:15:09.960
So I suddenly realized

00:15:12.240 --> 00:15:15.379
Meng Guangcai
is also part of this script,

00:15:16.740 --> 00:15:18.879
and he's just an actor too.

00:15:19.220 --> 00:15:20.360
So tell me,

00:15:22.000 --> 00:15:23.460
whom is Meng Guangcai

00:15:25.720 --> 00:15:27.080
acting for?

00:15:31.212 --> 00:15:32.360
(Construction Site, Beiyan County, 1993)

00:15:32.360 --> 00:15:34.519
Guangcai, I didn't want this either.

00:15:34.519 --> 00:15:37.220
But Dazhu insisted I get a gun.

00:15:37.220 --> 00:15:39.080
Can you shut up? I'll speak for myself.

00:15:39.259 --> 00:15:40.700
Well, if you're not using it,

00:15:40.700 --> 00:15:42.220
I'll just throw it in the river.

00:15:42.220 --> 00:15:43.879
Throw what?

00:15:45.639 --> 00:15:47.100
Guangcai, here's what I think.

00:15:47.100 --> 00:15:48.960
If something happens,

00:15:49.120 --> 00:15:51.840
we can use this to get us through.

00:15:51.840 --> 00:15:52.740
To get us through?

00:15:53.860 --> 00:15:55.220
Why are we doing this?

00:15:55.639 --> 00:15:57.320
Using a gun? If someone gets killed,

00:15:57.320 --> 00:15:58.460
everything changes then.

00:16:01.460 --> 00:16:04.259
I'm just thinking about our safety.

00:16:04.259 --> 00:16:05.820
Guangcai, should we keep it?

00:16:05.820 --> 00:16:06.700
We keep it if so.

00:16:06.700 --> 00:16:08.100
I'll have him throw it if not.

00:16:08.519 --> 00:16:11.840
Guangcai, whether to use the gun
is a big deal.

00:16:12.139 --> 00:16:13.360
You must think this through.

00:16:26.940 --> 00:16:27.860
Xiaoliang's life

00:16:29.440 --> 00:16:30.440
and Mr. Chen's life

00:16:32.320 --> 00:16:33.860
are both on us.

00:16:35.720 --> 00:16:36.639
Either we don't do it,

00:16:38.860 --> 00:16:40.320
or we make sure it's done.

00:16:49.440 --> 00:16:50.840
Qin.

00:16:56.320 --> 00:16:58.960
We do it, but not recklessly.

00:17:02.080 --> 00:17:03.960
They need evidence to arrest someone.

00:17:05.220 --> 00:17:06.579
With these train tickets,

00:17:07.380 --> 00:17:10.519
we can prove you weren't in Beiyan
during that time.

00:17:12.119 --> 00:17:13.579
That way, it's foolproof.

00:17:16.240 --> 00:17:17.519
It has to be foolproof.

00:17:25.079 --> 00:17:26.559
Even if we save Xiaoliang,

00:17:29.059 --> 00:17:30.500
he can't be without a father.

00:17:37.960 --> 00:17:38.740
It won't happen.

00:17:45.400 --> 00:17:48.819
Back then, you hopped the train
out of town to create an alibi.

00:17:50.519 --> 00:17:51.936
You actually fooled me for years

00:17:52.576 --> 00:17:54.720
with that one thing.

00:18:01.929 --> 00:18:07.320
(Train from Beiyan to Jinwan, 1993)

00:18:20.099 --> 00:18:20.839
Guangcai,

00:18:22.019 --> 00:18:22.740
we're here.

00:18:41.259 --> 00:18:42.299
To hell with it.

00:18:51.720 --> 00:18:52.460
Guangcai.

00:18:54.838 --> 00:18:58.779
(Jinwan Station)

00:18:58.779 --> 00:18:59.960
Move aside! Move!

00:19:00.259 --> 00:19:01.740
Huang Mantang still hasn't shown up.

00:19:01.740 --> 00:19:04.000
No idea if he got caught or ran off.

00:19:04.799 --> 00:19:06.440
Going back now is too risky, isn't it?

00:19:06.799 --> 00:19:08.799
Move aside! Move! Head out!

00:19:08.799 --> 00:19:10.220
We've done all we can.

00:19:11.240 --> 00:19:13.059
Going back now
is actually the safest move.

00:19:13.460 --> 00:19:14.339
Move aside! Move!

00:19:14.660 --> 00:19:16.000
Don't worry so much.

00:19:16.759 --> 00:19:19.880
I actually think
making some noise now is better.

00:19:20.339 --> 00:19:20.960
Noise?

00:19:21.200 --> 00:19:22.720
Noodles are ready, Guangcai.

00:19:25.720 --> 00:19:27.000
The train is coming in! Hurry!

00:19:27.500 --> 00:19:28.240
Coming! Coming!

00:19:30.140 --> 00:19:31.799
What are you two doing?
Move aside! Move!

00:19:40.480 --> 00:19:42.019
What are you doing? Watch out.

00:19:42.019 --> 00:19:44.339
Sorry, I-I wasn't paying attention.

00:19:44.500 --> 00:19:46.140
You got my clothes all dirty.

00:19:46.500 --> 00:19:48.400
I'm so sorry. It's my bad.

00:19:49.079 --> 00:19:50.519
I'll clean it all up later.

00:19:50.519 --> 00:19:51.740
Okay. Clean it up later.

00:19:51.900 --> 00:19:52.599
Alright.

00:19:52.599 --> 00:19:54.220
- Watch out next time.
- Okay.

00:19:56.299 --> 00:19:57.759
At the robbery scene,

00:20:00.220 --> 00:20:01.900
Xue Yonghui showed up unexpectedly.

00:20:03.660 --> 00:20:05.099
Though it was an accident,

00:20:06.220 --> 00:20:08.339
the job got done in the end.

00:20:09.599 --> 00:20:12.500
Then things were quiet for a few years.

00:20:13.900 --> 00:20:16.460
You took the stolen money
to the building materials market

00:20:16.839 --> 00:20:18.980
and started a business to launder it.

00:20:19.500 --> 00:20:20.800
But who knew

00:20:21.408 --> 00:20:23.839
the Hao brothers would show up then?

00:20:23.839 --> 00:20:25.480
Just like Zuo Long back in the day,

00:20:25.740 --> 00:20:28.099
they bullied you even worse.

00:20:28.099 --> 00:20:30.500
Then, at the right time,

00:20:31.839 --> 00:20:35.059
a fire broke out at Baima Market.

00:20:35.059 --> 00:20:36.299
Everyone knows

00:20:37.339 --> 00:20:41.319
that fire was an accident
caused by old wiring.

00:20:47.960 --> 00:20:49.740
Was it really an accident?

00:20:52.238 --> 00:20:53.480
(Beiyan County Hospital, 1999)

00:20:53.480 --> 00:20:54.599
(Baima Building Materials Market)
Fire! Quick!

00:20:54.680 --> 00:20:55.799
Quick! Fire!

00:20:55.839 --> 00:20:57.500
Fire! Put it out!

00:20:58.500 --> 00:21:00.000
Quick! Fire!

00:21:00.019 --> 00:21:01.500
- Put out the fire!
- Fire!

00:21:01.500 --> 00:21:02.400
Put out the fire!

00:21:02.579 --> 00:21:03.640
- Put out the fire!
- Fire!

00:21:03.880 --> 00:21:04.740
- Someone!
- Fire!

00:21:06.640 --> 00:21:08.400
- Fire!
- Come out and help!

00:21:08.400 --> 00:21:09.579
Put out the fire! Quick!

00:21:09.579 --> 00:21:11.480
Fire! Put it out!

00:21:11.480 --> 00:21:13.740
Put out the fire! Hurry!

00:21:13.740 --> 00:21:14.299
Hurry!

00:21:18.304 --> 00:21:21.536
(Authorized Personnel Only)

00:21:57.319 --> 00:22:00.000
Fire! Put it out!

00:22:00.380 --> 00:22:02.240
Quick! Fire!

00:22:02.559 --> 00:22:03.380
Help! Hurry!

00:22:04.579 --> 00:22:05.799
Put out the fire! Quick!

00:22:05.799 --> 00:22:08.599
- Put out the fire!
- Fire!

00:22:09.759 --> 00:22:11.000
- Put out the fire!
- Quick!

00:22:11.000 --> 00:22:11.980
Quick! Quick!

00:22:11.980 --> 00:22:13.839
Hurry! Everyone, hurry!

00:22:13.839 --> 00:22:15.220
Quick! Fire!

00:22:15.220 --> 00:22:16.640
Fire! Put it out!

00:22:16.940 --> 00:22:18.339
Fire! Put it out!

00:22:19.720 --> 00:22:20.660
Don't tell Guangcai.

00:22:30.200 --> 00:22:33.880
Zhu, you think too highly of me.

00:22:34.980 --> 00:22:36.720
I'm just a country woman.

00:22:40.819 --> 00:22:42.240
Then, in 2006,

00:22:46.759 --> 00:22:50.720
Huang Mantang, hooked on drugs,
suddenly came back to Beiyan.

00:22:52.000 --> 00:22:54.940
That's when you felt real danger.

00:22:59.759 --> 00:23:01.599
Guangcai, why come here?

00:23:05.500 --> 00:23:09.339
Starting today, we're doing something
very important here.

00:23:10.240 --> 00:23:11.240
What?

00:23:13.380 --> 00:23:17.259
We've hidden for years, always afraid
the police would find us.

00:23:20.059 --> 00:23:21.259
Starting today,

00:23:23.000 --> 00:23:24.799
we need to take some initiative.

00:23:28.980 --> 00:23:30.319
You once told me

00:23:31.500 --> 00:23:34.579
you don't remember who raped you.

00:23:35.140 --> 00:23:37.380
But you pointed suspicion
towards Zuo Long.

00:23:39.059 --> 00:23:40.740
So at the abandoned factory,

00:23:41.200 --> 00:23:43.599
when Huang Mantang
was about to reveal the truth,

00:23:44.500 --> 00:23:48.140
Xue Yonghui took the initiative
and killed him.

00:23:50.700 --> 00:23:52.200
Now, let's talk about Meng Guangcai.

00:23:54.000 --> 00:23:54.944
He knew perfectly well

00:23:56.000 --> 00:23:58.259
that even if he got lucky
and got out this time,

00:23:59.380 --> 00:24:01.019
I would keep watching him

00:24:02.140 --> 00:24:03.680
until I uncovered all the truth

00:24:04.704 --> 00:24:06.720
about the 6.10 case

00:24:07.839 --> 00:24:10.839
and revealed it to the world.

00:24:12.460 --> 00:24:16.140
Rather than that,
it's better to close the case now.

00:24:17.700 --> 00:24:18.740
Then why did he do that?

00:24:20.099 --> 00:24:23.339
What was he trying to hide,
or what was he trying to protect?

00:24:24.140 --> 00:24:27.019
Or was he trying to protect you?

00:24:30.259 --> 00:24:31.500
I didn't rob anyone.

00:24:32.500 --> 00:24:33.740
Why would they protect me?

00:24:35.500 --> 00:24:39.079
If you know the answer, you can tell me.

00:24:41.253 --> 00:24:46.035
(Outskirts of Shaguai Village,
Magou Town, 1999)

00:24:48.000 --> 00:24:50.539
Help! A pervert!

00:24:51.240 --> 00:24:51.799
Move!

00:24:51.799 --> 00:24:52.839
Help!

00:24:53.039 --> 00:24:54.539
Move! Move!

00:24:54.539 --> 00:24:55.200
Someone!

00:24:55.400 --> 00:24:58.700
You wretch! Meng Guangcai made me
do two years of hard time.

00:24:59.019 --> 00:25:00.660
I'll collect some interest from you.

00:25:00.660 --> 00:25:01.700
Help!

00:25:38.519 --> 00:25:39.339
Qin,

00:25:40.599 --> 00:25:43.740
did anyone see you
on your way back to the village?

00:25:44.640 --> 00:25:45.460
No.

00:25:47.079 --> 00:25:48.240
What do we do now?

00:25:49.099 --> 00:25:49.900
Serves him right.

00:25:51.720 --> 00:25:52.839
He did that to Qin.

00:25:53.720 --> 00:25:54.599
He deserved to die.

00:25:56.019 --> 00:25:57.339
Find a place to bury him.

00:25:57.839 --> 00:25:58.980
If this comes to light,

00:26:00.240 --> 00:26:01.319
put it on me.

00:26:09.059 --> 00:26:09.740
Xue Qin,

00:26:12.980 --> 00:26:14.720
we don't have direct evidence

00:26:16.900 --> 00:26:18.220
to convict Meng Guangcai.

00:26:20.599 --> 00:26:22.460
He could have just walked out.

00:26:24.720 --> 00:26:26.140
But he confessed voluntarily.

00:26:27.140 --> 00:26:30.500
He voluntarily confessed everything
and went to prison.

00:26:31.839 --> 00:26:33.900
The price is too high for him.

00:26:34.059 --> 00:26:35.460
There must be something

00:26:37.059 --> 00:26:38.640
that forced him to do that.

00:26:42.599 --> 00:26:44.200
If you know the answer,

00:26:47.799 --> 00:26:48.980
please tell me.

00:27:02.640 --> 00:27:03.480
Hello, Mom?

00:27:07.099 --> 00:27:09.339
Mom, Shaguai is fine.

00:27:09.839 --> 00:27:11.720
I want to stay with Grandpa
a few more days.

00:27:12.339 --> 00:27:13.660
We should get ready to leave.

00:27:15.460 --> 00:27:19.839
Mom, do you know
the old house is being demolished?

00:27:20.096 --> 00:27:21.600
They're building a high-speed rail.

00:27:23.059 --> 00:27:25.039
Mom, let me stay two more days, okay?

00:27:25.900 --> 00:27:26.839
I'm coming now.

00:27:54.200 --> 00:27:55.000
What is that?

00:28:00.519 --> 00:28:01.519
Stop! Stop!

00:28:02.839 --> 00:28:03.839
Stop! Stop!

00:28:04.599 --> 00:28:05.099
Get closer.

00:28:14.319 --> 00:28:15.140
What could it be?

00:28:15.279 --> 00:28:16.440
What good thing is it?

00:28:18.519 --> 00:28:19.539
Human bones! Human bones!

00:28:19.539 --> 00:28:20.680
Human bones! Human bones!

00:28:22.960 --> 00:28:23.960
This is a murder!

00:28:40.319 --> 00:28:42.339
Call the police! Call the police!

00:28:48.519 --> 00:28:51.839
I saw something nice
at the supply and marketing cooperative.

00:28:51.980 --> 00:28:53.660
I bought it for Qin.

00:28:54.480 --> 00:28:55.440
It's so pretty.

00:28:56.720 --> 00:28:58.000
Mr. Chen understands Qin best.

00:28:58.000 --> 00:28:59.339
Qin loves red.

00:29:18.299 --> 00:29:18.960
Master.

00:29:20.240 --> 00:29:21.140
Shaguai Village...

00:29:21.740 --> 00:29:23.339
A skeleton has been found there.

00:29:24.160 --> 00:29:25.500
It might be linked to Xue Qin.

00:29:26.000 --> 00:29:27.160
Find out where Xue Qin is.

00:29:27.339 --> 00:29:28.460
Find out where Xue Qin is.

00:29:33.099 --> 00:29:33.660
Master,

00:29:33.660 --> 00:29:35.460
what does the body
have to do with Xue Qin?

00:29:35.920 --> 00:29:38.099
Beside the skeleton
unearthed beneath their house,

00:29:38.099 --> 00:29:39.200
there was a red hairpin.

00:29:39.599 --> 00:29:42.140
Chen Rongfa remembers it was
a birthday gift he gave to Xue Qin.

00:29:57.460 --> 00:29:58.160
Faster!

00:30:19.960 --> 00:30:20.799
Catch up!

00:30:36.740 --> 00:30:37.579
Faster!

00:30:56.740 --> 00:30:57.940
Get ahead and cut her off!

00:31:57.099 --> 00:31:57.900
Xue Qin,

00:31:59.539 --> 00:32:00.500
Zuo Long has been found.

00:32:29.319 --> 00:32:31.019
The red hairpin Principal Chen gave you

00:32:33.559 --> 00:32:34.460
has also been found.

