00:34:00.160 --> 00:34:01.280
(negligent severe injury,)

00:34:01.280 --> 00:34:02.592
(and illegal possession of drugs,)

00:34:02.592 --> 00:34:03.737
(is sentenced to death.)

00:34:03.737 --> 00:34:05.697
